bug.short_desc: Table might me incorrectly formatted when displaying history

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 4592 screen shot
Steps to reproduce: 1. Import a Git project with some history 2. See History in OpenGrok
Actual result: Some projects have problem with table formatting due to a long length of revision and/or message comments. See attached screen shot. Especially column date is incorrectly formatted.
Used software: OpenGrok 0.10, Apache Tomcat 6.0.29, Sun Java 6 1.6.0_20-b02, Debian GNU/Linux 5.0.6, Mac OS X 10.7.1, Safari 5.1
This is UA specific and especially nothing can prevent safari from breaking these lines (because it doesn't know/handle related CSS3 properties). So not a bug.
